sequenceDiagram
    actor PublicUser
    participant SlotReservation
    participant DemoRequest
    participant AdminUser

    PublicUser->>SlotReservation: reserve(calcomReservationId: String)
    SlotReservation-->>PublicUser: Reservation confirmed
    PublicUser->>DemoRequest: submit(contactEmail: String, heardAboutUs: String)
    Note over DemoRequest: System may create/find User with temporary password\nand sends inquiry acknowledgement email
    DemoRequest-->>PublicUser: Inquiry submitted (status: PENDING)
    alt Approved by admin
        AdminUser->>DemoRequest: confirmBooking(calcomBookingId: String, meetingUrl: String)
        DemoRequest->>SlotReservation: markUsed()
    else Rejected by admin
        AdminUser->>DemoRequest: reject(reason: String)
        DemoRequest->>SlotReservation: release()
    end
